dungeons.name: Mount Ordeals - 8th Station
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his allies make for Baron Castle by boat to rescue Rosa when they run into trouble. Cicil washes ashore in Mysidia, from where he embarks on a quest to climb Mount Ordeals and become a Paladin.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Dark Knight without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Cecil's Darkness attack hits the whole party at once, kupo! Having someone with a Soul Break that can heal the entire party will make the fight a lot easier. Maybe you can even bring along a Roaming Warrior, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Cecil

dungeons.name: Mount Ordeals - Gravesite
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his allies make for Baron Castle by boat to rescue Rosa when they run into trouble. Cicil washes ashore in Mysidia, from where he embarks on a quest to climb Mount Ordeals and become a Paladin.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Scarmiglione's weakness to holy attacks.
Defeat Scarmiglione without using fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: Hit Scarmiglione with fire and he'll retaliate with Gas, hitting the whole party with debuffs! Even melee attacks can inspire him to sing a Cursed Elegy and slow your whole party, so watch out, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Scarmiglione
